Package: slopegraph
Version: 0.1.7
Title: Edward Tufte-Inspired Slopegraphs
Date: 2016-09-15
Authors@R: c(person("Thomas", "Leeper", role = c("aut","cre"),
                    email = "thosjleeper@gmail.com"))
Description: Convert a data.frame (containing a panel dataset, where rows are observations and columns are time periods) into an Edward Tufte-inspired slopegraph.
Imports: stats, graphics
Suggests: svglite
License: GPL-2
URL: https://github.com/leeper/slopegraph
